                  <h1 style="font-family:lucida grande,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:26px;line-height:28px;">It's Our Two Year Anniversary!</h1>
                  <p style="font-family:lucida grande,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:28px;color:#444444;">HAPPY NEW YEAR!</p>
                  <p style="font-family:lucida grande,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:28px;color:#444444;">2013 was a year of development and growth for both <strong style="color:#000;">Studio West</strong> and <strong style="color:#000;">Think Topography</strong>. There are a lot of changes in the works for both our coworking and software development businesses and we're absolutely giddy with excitment to roll them out to our members, clients, and the Ithaca community in the coming months!</p>
                  <p style="font-family:lucida grande,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:28px;color:#444444;">But first let me tell you about the party! You're officially invited to come celebrate two years of coworking with us on Friday, February 7 at Studio West. Please save the date on your calendar. There will be food, drink, live music, and of course, a great opportunity to meet and network with other energetic and creative Ithaca professionals.</p>
                  <p style="font-family:lucida grande,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:28px;color:#444444;">There's so much more news I'd like to share with you - like our new membership model and our on-site printing services - but we'll have plenty of time to talk about all of that at the party! Over the next few weeks, stay tuned for a new <a href="http://studiowestithaca.com">studiowestithaca.com</a> that breaks it all down and of course, please <a href="https://www.facebook.com/studiowestithaca">like our Facebook page</a>, if you haven't already, to stay up to date as we announce these new developments.</p>
                  <p style="font-family:lucida grande,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:28px;color:#444444;">Here's to an amazing 2014, <%= @user.first_name %>. Let's make it happen!</p>
